data.description: House hacking opportunity! Live in one unit while collecting rent on the 3 remaining units. This income producing quadplex with lots of potential for increase as rents in the area have increased ~15% since 2022 and are continuing to increase. Parking included behind the building, with a gated entrance. Don't miss out on the chance to get this cash flowing property with lots of property add! All information to be verified by buyer and buyer agent. This property consists of two different structures, each containing two units.
